description: Suddenly, a beautiful girl came falling naked from the sky. Without previous memory and calling herself "Yagyuu Jubei", still naked approached http://anidb.net/ch19205 [Muneakira] calling him "Onii-chan" (Big brother) with spontaneous Imouto-chara (little sister characterization). However, triggered by a certain event, another "Jubei" personality awakened releasing innumerable dreadful secret techniques. Her outward appearance is (around) of a high school student.
name: Yagyuu Juubee
